				<h3>Making a Decision</h3>
				<h4>How much do these medicines cost?</h4>
<p>The cost to you depends on several things, including:</p>
<ul>
	<li>What type of insurance plan you have and what medicines it covers.</li>
	<li>How much medicine you need.</li>
	<li>Whether you use generic or brand-name medicines.</li>
</ul>
